WITH THE VENTURA
COUNTY SHERIFF'S DEPARTMENT,

28:53.601 --> 28:55.037
ANDY'S HAD TWO COUNTS

28:55.168 --> 28:56.952
OF EXCESSIVE USE OF FORCE
